<h1 class='property-title'>orphans</h1>
<p class='property-description'>The <code>orphans</code> <a title="CSS" rel="internal" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en/CSS">CSS</a> property refers to the <em>minimum</em> number of lines in a block container that must be left at the bottom of the page.&nbsp; This property is normally used to control how page breaks occur.</p>